item.title: CVE-2022-28770|2024-08-03T06:03:52.600Z -- sap%20se -- sapui5%20%28vbm%20library%29
item.description: Due to insufficient input validation, SAPUI5 library(vbm) - versions 750, 753, 754, 755, 75, allows an unauthenticated attacker to inject a script into the URL and execute code. On successful exploitation, an attacker can view or modify information causing a limited impact on confidentiality and integrity of the application.
